<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Four <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">architrave</rs> blocks, complete (b, c) or in fragments (a, d) incorporating architrave and <rs type="decoration">frieze</rs>, but without decoration. a: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.62</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.66</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.22</measure>; b: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">1.61</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.63</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.58</measure>; c: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">1.83</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.68</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.54</measure>; d: <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">1.20</measure> + <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">1.22</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.65</measure>   × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.57</measure>.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text"><head>Description of Text</head><p> The first line of the inscription is cut on the area of the frieze; the second and third lines are cut on the first and second fasciae of the architrave, below a simple moulding.</p></div><div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
